produce%20summaries%20of%20what%20I%20said%20to%20it%2C%20Suki%20generates%20a%20summarizing%20note%20from%20the%20appointment%2C%20which%20I%20send%20to%20my%20computer.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20my%20phone%20dies%20or%20I%20don't%20have%20it%20on%20me%2C%20I%20can%20speak%20directly%20to%20Suki%20about%20the%20appointment.%20It%20creates%20a%20solid%20note%20as%20if%20it%20were%20listening%20to%20the%20exam%20room%20interaction%2C%20but%20I%20think%20it's%20more%20accurate%20when%20I%20have%20it%20in%20the%20room%20with%20the%20patient.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20I'll%20spend%2015%20minutes%20going%20through%20my%20notes%20on%20my%20computer%2C%20making%20sure%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-down-rounds-rise-valuations-investors-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20AI%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20spelled%20the%20drugs%20correctly%2C%20and%20cleaning%20things%20up.%20It's%20a%20huge%20contrast%20from%20the%2010%20hours%20a%20week%20I%20used%20to%20spend%20on%20notetaking.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI'm%20very%20legal-minded%2C%20and%20one%20of%20my%20first%20questions%20about%20Suki%20was%20how%20long%20it%20stores%20patient%20information.%20I%20learned%20that%20the%20audio%20and%20transcript%20from%20patient%20interactions%20are%20erased%20from%20Suki%20after%20seven%20days%2C%20so%20I%20felt%20comfortable%20with%20how%20it%20handles%20privacy.%20Before%20the%20notes%20are%20erased%20from%20Suki%2C%20I%20send%20them%20to%20my%20computer%2C%20and%20they're%20permanently%20stored%20in%20my%20electronic%20records.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22390a5732-407e-48d8-9ff6-68fd25bc4a68%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EUsing%20AI%20at%20work%20has%20reduced%20my%20stress%2C%20but%20the%20technology%20isn't%20perfect%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20use%20Suki%20all%20the%20time%20now.%20I%20pay%20for%20the%20service%2C%20which%20is%20deducted%20from%20my%20paycheck.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt's%20made%20my%20workflow%20easier.%20I'm%20more%20able%20to%20accommodate%20patients%20into%20my%20schedule.%20Patients%20have%20also%20noticed%20that%20I%20don't%20have%20to%20type%20anymore%20and%20can%20keep%20eye%20contact%20without%20looking%20over%20a%20computer.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt's%20alleviated%20stress%20in%20my%20personal%20life.%20I'd%20never%20miss%20family%20events%20for%20work%20because%20family%20is%20my%20priority%2C%20but%20I%20did%20overload%20myself%20and%20would%20have%20to%20stay%20up%20late%20to%20finish%20notes.%20Now%2C%20when%20I'm%20home%2C%20my%20family%20and%20I%20are%20watching%20movies%20or%20doing%20homework%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20have%20to%20type%20notes%20for%20work%20on%20my%20laptop.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20technology%20isn't%20perfect.%20Sometimes%2C%20when%20it%20generated%20notes%2C%20there%20were%20two%20paragraphs%20that%20almost%20said%20the%20same%20thing%2C%20so%20I'd%20cut%20one%20out%20when%20editing.%20Every%20now%20and%20then%2C%20it%20will%20misunderstand%20a%20medicine%20I%20say%20and%20put%20in%20something%20else.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20don't%20see%20this%20as%20a%20problem.%20There%20are%20plenty%20of%20errors%20with%20scribbly%20doctor's%20handwriting%20and%20some%20with%20other%20dictation%20software.%20As%20physicians%2C%20we're%20responsible%20for%20reviewing%20notes%20for%20accuracy.%20With%20any%20technology%2C%20there%20will%20be%20an%20acceptable%20degree%20of%20edits%20that%20need%20to%20be%20made.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22994fc1a5-2b7a-4345-9a6e-73e00286e83f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EI'm%20in%20favor%20of%20using%20AI%20for%20transcription%20and%20cautiously%20welcome%20it%20in%20other%20medical%20areas%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.b