d.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Feuler-motors-forays-into-lcv-segment-drives-in-two-electric-models-124092500536_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Feuler-motors-forays-into-lcv-segment-drives-in-two-electric-models-124092500536_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Feuler-motors-forays-into-lcv-segment-drives-in-two-electric-models-124092500536_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22An%20ex-Twitter%20employee%20won%20a%20legal%20battle%20over%20unpaid%20severance.%20Experts%20say%20it%20could%20spark%20more%20claims.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225143%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Elon%20Musk%20next%20to%20Twitter's%20logo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f29ef2ce3009a0fac8cb6a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223429%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EElon%20Musk%20took%20over%20Twitter%20in%20October%202022.%3Cp%3EAnadolu%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAn%20ex-Twitter%20employee%20won%20a%20legal%20battle%20through%20arbitration%20over%20unpaid%20severance%2C%20per%20Bloomberg.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELegal%20experts%20say%20it%20may%20prompt%20X%20to%20handle%20similar%20cases%20consistently%20and%20consider%20settling%20disputes.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20case%20follows%20Elon%20Musk's%202022%20takeover%20of%20Twitter%2C%20now%20called%20X%2C%20and%20subsequent%20layoffs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20former%20Twitter%20employee's%20victory%20in%20a%20legal%20dispute%20over%20unpaid%20severance%20could%20prompt%20more%20ex-staff%20to%20pursue%20cases%20against%20the%20social%20media%20company%2C%20legal%20experts%20have%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ex-Twitter%20worker%2C%20who%20was%20laid%20off%20during%20the%20chaotic%20aftermath%20of%20Elon%20Musk's%20takeover%20of%20the%20social%20media%20platform%2C%20won%20the%20case%20after%20it%20was%20handled%20through%20a%20closed-door%20arbitration%2C%20according%20to%20a%20memo%20obtained%20by%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-09-23%2Fex-twitter-worker-wins-musk-layoff-pay-fight-memo-says%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Bloomberg%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20decision%20comes%20nearly%20two%20years%20after%20Elon%20Musk%20completed%20a%20%2444%20billion%20takeover%20of%20Twitter%20and%20then%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-twitter-recruiting-layoffs-staff-workers-firing-employees-workforce-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Elaid%20off%20around%20half%20the%20company's%20staff%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0a%20week%20later.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20Twitter%20employee's%20lawyer%2C%20Shannon%20Liss-Riordan%2C%20reportedly%20said%20in%20the%20memo%20that%20her%20client%20was%20awarded%20the%20full%20severance%20package%20and%20that%20she%20expects%20more%20rulings%20to%20come%20out%20in%20the%20following%20months.%20There%20are%2015%20other%20cases%20that%20have%20also%20had%20arbitration%20hearings%2C%20per%20the%20memo%20seen%20by%20Bloomberg.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ex-Twitter%20worker's%20win%20is%20the%20first%20of%20what%20experts%20say%20could%20lead%20to%20many%20more%20similar%20resolutions.%20It%20might%20raise%20hope%20for%20other%20former%20employees%20who%20feel%20their%20severance%20agreements%20were%20mishandled%20during%20Musk's%20tumultuous%20restructuring%20of%20Twitter%2C%20now%20called%20X.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJamie%20E.%20Wright%2C%20labor%20attorney%20and%20founder%20of%20The%20Wright%20Law%20Firm%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20arbitration%20ruling%20could%20inspire%20ex-Twitter%20staffers%20who%20%26quot%3Blodged%20comparable%20arbitration%20claims%20to%20pursue%20their%20cases%20further.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220f3ab6a7-009d-4b42-948a-3c1506cd67b7%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt%20could%20encourage%20Musk%20to%20settle%20with%20other%20former%20employees%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20the%20outcome%20is%20not%20a%20binding%20precedent%20like%20a%20court%20ruling%2C%20Russel%20Morgan%2C%20principal%20and%20founder%20of%20Morgan%20Legal%20Group%2C%20told%20BI%20it%20could%20still%20persuade%20companies%20to%20align%20with%20it.%20Such%20arbitration%20rulings%20could%20help%20%26quot%3Bmove%20the%20dial%26quot%3B%20in%20similar%20cases%2C%20he%20added.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20could%20set%20a%20precedent%20for%20all%20the%20other%20employees%20claiming%20they%20are%20still%20owed%20money%20and%20pressure%20the%20social%20media%20company%20to%20settle%2C%26quot%3B%20Morgan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20should%20also%20consider%20settling%20with%20others%20with%20similar%20complaints%20to%20avoid%20taking%20a%20reputational%20hit%20and%20incurring%20expenses%20from%20more%20legal%20battles%2C%20Wright%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EX%20and%20Musk%20are%20also%20facing%20a%20lawsuit%20over%20severance%20terms%20from%20100%20former%20Twitter%20workers%20who%20were%20fired%20in%202022.%20Lisa%20Bloom%2C%20the%20attorney%20representing%20the%20group%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20BI%20that%20they%20%26quot%3Bapplaud%26quot%3B%20the%20arbitrator's%20decision%20and%20encouraged%20Musk%20to%20%26quot%3Bdo%20the%20right%20thing%20now%20and%20pay%20the%20workers%20who%20built%20Twitter%20what%20they%20were%20promised.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBloom%20said%20they%20are%20still%20aggressively%20pursuing%20their%20cases%20and%20have%20scheduled%20individual%20arbitration%20hearings%20for%20each%20of%20the%20clients.%20The%20hearings%20will%20begin%20in%20December%202024%20and%20run%20through%20August%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222b37aa08-6d27-478e-8cc2-7495a32b9d26%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMusk%20avoided%20a%20%24500%20million%20severance%20pay%20lawsuit%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20July%2C%20a%20federal%20judge%20in%20the%20Northern%20District%20of%20California%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjudge-ruled-in-favor-elon-musk-saving-x-500-million-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edismissed%20a%20lawsuit%20from%20former%20Twitter%20employees%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20claimed%20the%20company%20owed%20%24500%20million%20severance%20to%20around%206%2C000%20laid-off%20workers.%20The%20judge%20ultimately%20found%20insufficient%20facts%20to%20support%20the%20claim%20that%20the%20Employee%20Retirement%20Income%20Security%20Act%20(ERISA)%2C%20a%20federal%20law%2C%20governs%20the%20severance%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWeeks%20after%20Musk%20took%20over%20the%20company%2C%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-twitter-unfair-dismissal-case-learnings-for-workers-employers-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esent%20out%20a%20companywide%20email%3C%2Fa%3E%20giving%20employees%20a%20stark%20choice%3A%20either%20sign%20up%20to%20work%20at%20an%20%26quot%3Bextremely%20hardcore%26quot%3B%20rate%20and%20help%20build%20%26quot%3BTwitter%202.0%26quot%3B%20or%20resign.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20will%20mean%20working%20long%20hours%20at%20high%20intensity%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20wrote%20in%20the%20email.%20%26quot%3BOnly%20exceptional%20performance%20will%20constitute%20a%20passing%20grade.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20anyone%20who%20didn't%20click%20yes%20on%20an%20attached%20Google%20form%20by%20the%20next%20day%20would%20receive%20three%20months%20of%20severance%20pay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGary%20Rooney%2C%20a%20former%20Twitter%20employee%2C%20was%20laid%20off%20after%20he%20didn't%20respond%20to%20the%20email%20and%20brought%20his%20case%20to%20Ireland's%20Workplace%20Relations%20Commission.%20In%20August%2C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftwitter-employee-unfair-dismissal-elon-musk-hardcore-demand-8-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Rooney%20won%20the%20unfair%20dismissal%20case%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20was%20awarded%20about%20%24600%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Musk%20and%20X%2C%20the%20question%20remains%20whether%20they%20fight%20each%20case%20or%20find%20a%20way%20to%20settle%20what%20might%20be%20a%20brewing%20storm%20of%20claims.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ELiss-Riordan%20declined%20to%20comment.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EX%20didn't%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fex-twitter-employee-wins-unpaid-severance-dispute-elon-musk-takeover-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727257107000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f29f7dd17aa3c7b2b554ea%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fex-twitter-employee-wins-unpaid-severance-dispute-elon-musk-takeover-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20former%20Twitter%20employee%20won%20an%20arbitration%20case%20over%20unpaid%20severance.%20Experts%20say%20it%20could%20prompt%20X%20to%20handle%20similar%20cases%20consistently.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jmann%40insider.com%20(Jyoti%20Mann)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fex-twitter-employee-wins-unpaid-severance-dispute-elon-musk-takeover-2024-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Shriram%20Finance%20raises%20%24500%20million%20from%20investors%20via%20USD%20Social%20Bonds%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727256670000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fassets%2Fweb-assets%2Fimages%2FBusiness_Standard_685x385.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fshriram-finance-raises-500-million-from-investors-via-usd-social-bonds-124092500602_1.html%22%2C%22summary%2