20houses%20are%20now%20hiring%20ice-cream%20trucks%20to%20lure%20prospective%20buyers%20into%20properties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sudden%20shift%20in%20Austin's%20real-estate%20market%20can%20be%20read%20in%20two%20ways.%20Look%20at%20it%20through%20one%20lens%2C%20and%20it's%20a%20cautionary%20tale%20in%20which%20FOMO-filled%20buyers%20irrationally%20bid%20up%20home%20prices%2C%20setting%20the%20stage%20for%20an%20inevitable%20bust.%20Look%20at%20it%20another%20way%2C%20though%2C%20and%20it's%20a%20success%20story%20of%20a%20growing%20city%3A%20Real-estate%20developers%20saw%20all%20those%20millennials%20and%20out-of-towners%20clamoring%20for%20a%20piece%20of%20Austin%20and%20answered%20the%20call%2C%20building%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20new%20homes%20in%20just%20a%20few%20years.%20The%20construction%20boom%2C%20combined%20with%20spiking%20mortgage%20rates%2C%20kept%20prices%20from%20spiraling%20further%20out%20of%20control.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20Econ%20101%20happened.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20isn't%20a%20bust%20in%20the%20traditional%20sense%20%E2%80%94%20pretty%20much%20anyone%20who%20owned%20a%20home%20in%20Austin%20before%202020%20is%20substantially%20richer%20today%20than%20they%20were%20a%20few%20years%20ago.%20But%20as%20other%20pandemic%20Zoomtowns%20continue%20to%20see%20increases%20in%20prices%20and%20rents%2C%20Austin%20stands%20alone%20in%20its%20change%20of%20fortune.%20The%20reversal%20has%20meant%20short-term%20pain%20for%20homebuyers%20who%20bought%20near%20the%20peak%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhome-sellers-summer-disappointment-mortgage-rates-house-prices-real-estate-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edisappointed%20sellers%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20now%20expect%20smaller%20windfalls%2C%20and%20homebuilders%20who%20are%20eager%20to%20offload%20their%20inventory.%20But%20letting%20some%20air%20out%20of%20the%20bubble%20will%20turn%20out%20to%20be%20a%20great%20thing%20for%20Austin%20in%20the%20long%20run.