%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20shortage%20of%20ambition%20among%20Austin's%20homebuilders%2C%20however.%20Their%20efforts%20may%20have%20been%20focused%20on%20chasing%20all%20the%20profit%20that%20comes%20with%20a%20crush%20of%20demand%2C%20but%20they%20ended%20up%20doing%20what%20hopeful%20buyers%20had%20been%20praying%20for%20%E2%80%94%20bringing%20down%20home%20prices.%20The%20typical%20home%20price%20in%20Austin%20was%20down%20almost%204%25%20in%20July%20compared%20with%20the%20same%20month%20in%202023%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Freddie%20Mac%20House%20Price%20Index%2C%20while%20prices%20across%20the%20US%20were%20up%20more%20than%204%25.%20On%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20a%20single-digit%20drop%20like%20Austin's%20%26quot%3Bis%20not%20a%20huge%20number%2C%26quot%3B%20Sean%20Kelly-Rand%2C%20a%20Boston%20lender%20who%20works%20with%20home%20developers%2C%20told%20me%2C%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20that's%20massive.%26quot%3B%20Overall%2C%20Austin%20home%20prices%20are%20down%20more%20than%2014%25%20from%20the%20peak%20in%202022%2C%20according%20to%20Freddie%20Mac%2C%20and%20more%20than%2018%25%20according%20to%20Zillow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FXyOzn%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Zillow%20home%20value%20index%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22437%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EHomeowners%20and%20-builders%20don't%20like%20to%20see%20price%20drops%20%E2%80%94%20they%20want%20to%20watch%20their%20wealth%20balloon%20and%20reap%20the%20rewards%20of%20a%20market%20that's%20running%20red%20hot.%20But%20just%20like%20a%20collapse%20in%20prices%20is%20bad%20news%20for%20everyone%2C%20an%20unsustainable%20run-up%20in%20home%20values%20is%20also%20unhealthy.%20Companies%20don't%20want%20to%20move%20to%20a%20place%20where%20workers%20can't%20afford%20to%20live.%20Wannabe%20sellers%20might%20choose%20to%20stay%20in%20homes%20they've%20outgrown%20if%20they%20can't%20find%20anything%20else%20within%20their%20budget.%20Add%20up%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsan-francisco-doom-loop-fix-american-city-housing-transit-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eall%20these%20problems%20and%20you%20get%20San%20Francisco%3C%2Fa%3E.%20A%20crash%20in%20home%20prices%20would've%20also%20been%20bad%20news%20for%20Austin%2C%20sure%2C%20but%20that's%20not%20what's%20going%20on%20here.%20The%20vast%20majority%20of%20homeowners%20in%20Austin%20are%20still%20wealthier%20than%20they%20were%20before%20all%20this%20craziness%2C%20and%20local%20homebuilders%20made%20plenty%20of%20hay%20while%20the%20sun%20was%20shining.%20For%20that%20reason%2C%20Austin's%20slowdown%20isn't%20a%20doom%20signal%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20a%20dazzling%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20nice%20to%20see%20the%20positive%20developments%20in%20Austin%2C%26quot%3B%20Orphe%20Divounguy%2C%20a%20senior%20economist%20at%20Zillow%2C%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BAustin%20should%20be%20a%20model%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country%20in%20terms%20of%20allowing%20builders%20to%20meet%20demand.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EAustin's%20long-standing%20advantages%20were%20on%20full%20display%20during%20the%20building%20boom%3A%20Sun%20Belt%20cities%20in%20the%20lower%20half%20of%20the%20US%20have%20traditionally%20been%20more%20permissive%20of%20growth%2C%20which%20enabled%20developers%20to%20mobilize%20when%20they%20saw%20the%20first%20signs%20of%20Austin's%20unprecedented%20spike%20in%20home%20values.%20And%20most%20of%20the%20new%20construction%20was%20concentrated%20in%20the%20suburbs%2C%20where%20there%20was%20plenty%20of%20space%20to%20build%20outward.%20Not%20all%20cities%20have%20the%20luxury%20of%20ample%20space%2C%20but%20they%20do%20have%20the%20power%20to%20cut%20red%20tape%20and%20make%20it%20easier%20to%20build%20more%20types%20of%20housing.%20When%20developers%20can%20get%20projects%20approved%20more%20quickly%2C%20they're%20more%20responsive%20to%20buyer%20demand%2C%20which%20prevents%20prices%20from%20getting%20out%20of%20hand.%20Relaxing%20the%20zoning%20laws%2C%20which%20tell%20builders%20what%20they%20can%20and%20can't%20build%2C%20allows%20developers%20to%20get%20creative%20and%20add%20multiple%20housing%20units%20to%20lots%20that%20might%20have%20traditionally%20allowed%20only%20single-family%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENobody%20watching%20the%20Austin%20market%20should%20be%20having%20flashbacks%20to%20the%20Great%20Recession.%20The%20market's%20cooling%20is%20less%20a%20disturbing%20sign%20of%20cratering%20demand%20and%20more%20a%20hopeful%20hint%20that%20the%20city%20can%20adapt%20to%20people's%20desire%20to%20call%20it%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20Austin%20is%20going%20to%20be%20fine%20in%20the%20medium%20to%20long%20run%2C%26quot%3B%20Jenny%20Schuetz%2C%20a%20housing-policy%20expert%20at%20the%20Brookings%20Institution%2C%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BThe%20fundamentals%20of%20Austin's%20economy%20are%20great%2C%20and%20it's%20going%20to%20continue%20to%20grow%20with%20jobs%20and%20population%20over%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20easing%20the%20housing%20crunch%20will%20probably%20add%20to%20Austin's%20allure%2C%20which%20has%20always%20been%20at%20least%20partly%20predicated%20on%20being%20cheaper%20than%20the%20big%20cities%20on%20the%20coasts.%20The%20next%20challenge%20will%20be%20to%20avoid%20forfeiting%20this%20success%20%E2%80%94%20homebuilding%20is%20prone%20to%20cycles%20of%20booms%20and%20busts%2C%20and%20developers%20are%20already%20pulling%20back%20on%20new%20construction%20as%20they%20try%20to%20get%20their%20already-built%20units%20off%20their%20books.%20Home%20prices%20in%20Austin%20may%20be%20down%20year%20over%20year%20today%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20like%20there's%20a%20glut%20of%20empty%20homes%20like%20there%20was%20around%20the%20country%20in%202008.%20If%20building%20in%20Austin%20dries%20up%2C%20prices%20may%20very%20well%20resume%20their%20rise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKelly-Rand%2C%20the%20Boston%20lender%2C%20thought%20about%20making%20inroads%20in%20Austin%20a%20few%20years%20ago%20when%20the%20building%20renaissance%20was%20in%20full%20swing.%20But%20ultimately%2C%20he%20decided%20not%20to%20%E2%80%94%20buyers'%20behavior%20was%20too%20frenzied%20for%20his%20taste%2C%20and%20prices%20seemed%20likely%20to%20come%20down%20when%20all%20those%20homes%20on%20the%20horizon%20actually%20got%20built.%20Nevertheless%2C%20Kelly-Rand%20told%20me%20he's%20still%20a%20believer%20in%20the%20Texas%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLong%20term%2C%20I%20think%20Austin%20will%20be%20in%20an%20even%20better%20position%2C%26quot%3B%20Kelly-Rand%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20right%20thing%20is%20happening%20in%20that%20developers%20are%20meeting%20demand.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Fjames-rodriguez%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3EJames%20Rodriguez%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20reporter%20on%20Business%20Insider's%20Discourse%20team.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faustin-home-prices-falling-texas-mortgage-rates-housing-crisis-success-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727256242000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f3271bd17aa3c7b2b5bf75%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faustin-home-prices-falling-texas-mortgage-rates-housing-crisis-success-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Home%20prices%20and%20rents%20are%20down%20significantly%20in%20Austin%2C%20a%20pandemic-era%20boomtown.%20But%20the%20slowdown%20is%20actually%20a%20sign%20of%20a%20healthy%20market.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jrodriguez%40insider.com%20(James%20Rodriguez)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faustin-home-prices-falling-texas-mortgage-rates-housing-crisis-success-2024-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sam%20Altman%20believes%20wars%20will%20be%20fought%20over%20AI%20unless%20there's%20massive%20spending%20on%20infrastructure.%20But%20that%20comes%20with%20a%20cost.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225100%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20photo%20illustration%20of%20robotic%20androids%20towering%20over%20a%20futuristic%20city.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f33f5ad17aa3c7b2b5c76d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223187%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELeaders%20in%20the%20AI%20industry%20are%20calling%20for%20massive%20investments%20to%20create%20enough%20infrastructure%20to%20develop%20the%20technology.%20Experts%20warn%20the%20development%20will%20come%20with%20a%20high%20social%20and%20environmental%20cost.%3Cp%3EEducation%20Images%2FUniversal%20Images%20Group%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EOpenAI%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%2C%20in%20a%20Monday%20blog%20post%2C%20called%20for%20massive%20investments%20in%20AI%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EInsufficient%20infrastructure%2C%20Altman%20warned%2C%20will%20lead%20to%20wars%20being%20fought%20over%20the%20technology.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20experts%20say%20developing%20AI%20infrastructure%20at%20scale%20comes%20with%20big%20social%20and%20environmental%20costs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20Monday%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fia.samaltman.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblog%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20OpenAI%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%20argued%20that%20massive%20investment%20in%20AI%20infrastructure%20is%20key%20to%20market%20dominance%20%E2%80%94%20and%20avoiding%20global%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20want%20to%20put%20AI%20into%20the%20hands%20of%20as%20many%20people%20as%20possible%2C%20we%20need%20to%20drive%20down%20the%20cost%20of%20compute%20and%20make%20it%20abundant%20(which%20requires%20lots%20of%20energy%20and%20chips)%2C%26quot%3B%20Altman%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BIf%20we%20don't%20build%20enough%20infrastructure%2C%20AI%20will%20be%20a%20very%20limited%20resource%20that%20wars%20get%20fought%20over%2C%20and%20that%20becomes%20mostly%20a%20tool%20for%20rich%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20promoting%20the%20development%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerica-ai-infrastructure-data-center-microsoft-blackrock-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20infrastructure%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20the%20new%20focus%20of%20industry%20leaders%20like%20Altman%2C%20researchers%20on%20the%20technology's%20social%2C%20environmental%2C%20and%20economic%20impacts%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20development%20of%20the%20data%20centers%20and%20hardware%20systems%20needed%20to%20achieve%20artificial%20general%20intelligence%20or%20superintelligence%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewill%20cost%20far%20more%20than%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20OpenAI%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2271040451-7ee2-4474-ac54-2c383f024bc4%5C%22%3EA%20sharp%20industry%20focus%20on%20AI%20infrastructure%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20hot%20topic%20in%20artificial%20intelligence%20is%20infrastructure%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0investing%20in%20it%2C%20planning%20a%20massive%20expansion%20of%20computing%20power%2C%20and%20creating%20the%20data%20centers%20needed%20to%20develop%20the%20technology%20at%20scale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20Microsoft%20and%20BlackRock%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.microsoft.com%2F2024%2F09%2F17%2Fblackrock-global-infrastructure-partners-microsoft-and-mgx-launch-new-ai-partnership-to-invest-in-data-centers-and-supporting-power-infrastructure%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20launch%20of%20a%20%2430%20billion%20fund%20to%20%26quot%3Benhance%20American%20competitiveness%20in%20AI%20while%20meeting%20the%20growing%20need%20for%20energy%20infrastructure%20to%20power%20economic%20growth.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20the%20White%20House%20hosted%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fbriefing-room%2Fstatements-releases%2F2024%2F09%2F12%2Freadout-of-white-house-roundtable-on-u-s-leadership-in-ai-infrastructure%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eroundtable%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20AI%20infrastructure%20leaders%20from%20around%20the%20country%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Altman%20and%20executives%20from%20Microsoft%2C%20Meta%2C%20Amazon%2C%20and%20Anthropic%2C%20among%20others%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0to%20%26quot%3Bdiscuss%20steps%20to%20ensure%20the%20United%20States%20continues%20to%20lead%20the%20world%20in%20AI%26quot%3B%20and%20ensure%20the%20tech's%20development%20is%20aligned%20with%20%26quot%3Bnational%20security%2C%20economic%2C%20and%20environmental%20goals.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20experts%20are%20cautiously%20optimistic%20about%20AI%2C%20others%20pointed%20to%20pitfalls%20in%20the%20rapid%20build-up%20of%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220aa9a51a-d85a-46f5-bd85-fb71b3470c95%5C%22%3EAI's%20unclear%20economic%20benefits%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAlex%20de%20Vries%2C%20an%20economist%20and%20the%20founder%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdigiconomist.net%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDigiconomist%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20platform%20dedicated%20to%20exposing%20the%20unintended%20consequences%20of%20digital%20trends%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20the%20current%20conversation%20on%20AI%20infrastructure%20is%20focused%20on%20the%20development%20of%20large-scale%20data%20centers%2C%20with%20ind