0model%20that%20can%20do%20it%20all%2C%20Ren%20said%20he%20believes%20the%20industry%20needs%20to%20focus%20on%20smaller%2C%20more%20specialized%20models%20that%20require%20fewer%20resources%20and%20can%20be%20built%20to%20handle%20more%20precise%C2%A0tasks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20we%20need%20to%20shift%20the%20way%20we%20build%20AI%2C%20not%20just%20rely%20on%20bigger%20and%20bigger%20models%2C%26quot%3B%20Ren%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20really%20sustainable%20or%20scalable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2253158441-3f88-40ef-a72f-35691ba29f3a%5C%22%3EAn%20environmental%20disaster%20in%20the%20making%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20de%20Vries%20and%20Ren%20said%20that%20beyond%20the%20financial%20costs%2C%20ensuring%20AI%20infrastructure%20is%20developed%20at%20the%20scale%20industry%20players%20like%20Altman%20seek%20comes%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-generative-ai-environment-climate-change-global-emissions-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emassive%20environmental%20costs%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20talking%20about%20large-scale%20data%20centers%2C%20they%20are%20going%20to%20be%20consuming%20a%20huge%20amount%20of%20power%20and%20a%20huge%20amount%20of%20water%2C%26quot%3B%20de%20Vries%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20noted%20that%20data%20centers%20consume%20tons%20of%20water%20for%20their%20cooling%20systems%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0some%20of%20which%20evaporates%2C%20so%20it%20cannot%20be%20reused.%20Electricity%20consumption%20also%20skyrockets%2C%20driving%20up%20demand%20and%20increasing%20reliance%20on%20fossil%20fuels%20despite%20the%20industry's%20use%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-the-6-billion-market-for-renewable-energy-certificates-2020-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erenewable%20energy%20certificates%20(RECs)%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWind%20and%20solar%20companies%20generate%20RECs%20for%20each%20