er%20list%20of%20cons.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThe%20main%20challenge%20is%20the%20discomfort%20of%20doing%20things%20differently%20and%20taking%20ownership%20of%20tasks%20that%20have%20been%20covered%20by%209-to-5s%20traditionally%2C%20like%20managing%20finances%2C%20taxes%2C%20healthcare%2C%20and%20client%20acquisition%2C%26quot%3B%20Dixon%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20she%20emphasized%20that%20there%20are%20solutions.%20For%20example%2C%20she%20partners%20with%20a%20professional%20who%20helps%20her%20freelancers%20and%20entrepreneurs%20obtain%20appropriate%20health%20coverage.%20And%20for%20freelancers%20who%20feel%20their%20lifestyle%20is%20too%20insular%2C%20Dixon%20encourages%20them%20to%20attend%20holistic%20events%20and%20experiences%20to%20connect%20with%20others.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226b4be105-894b-475b-9fcb-f5265c21f717%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EWorkers%20need%20to%20learn%20more%20to%20earn%20more%20as%20freelancers%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20short%20term%2C%20these%20colossal%20workplace%20changes%20will%20create%20new%20challenges%2C%20some%20of%20which%20we're%20already%20seeing.%20As%20Dixon%20puts%20it%2C%20just%20getting%20an%20interview%20feels%20a%20little%20like%20%26quot%3BThe%20Hunger%20Games.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlso%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20rise%20of%20AI%20and%20automation%20means%20that%20many%20traditional%20jobs%20may%20not%20exist%20in%20the%20coming%20years%20%E2%80%94%20particularly%20in%20service%20industries.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20this%20in%20mind%2C%20Dixon%20suggested%20leaning%20into%20reskilling%20and%20upskilling%2C%20knowing%20that%20in%20this%20field%2C%20the%20more%20you%20learn%2C%20the%20more%20you%20earn.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2245b1b179-c089-4b9d-9f60-7ba73e8dd4