%20result%3A%20Klarity%20unlocked%20new%20levels%20of%20automation%20for%20processes%20that%20were%20previously%20done%20by%20people%20%E2%80%94%20increasing%20its%20pass-through%20rate%20to%2085%25%20%E2%80%94%20and%20sped%20up%20its%20ability%20to%20ship%20features.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20took%20notice.%20In%20June%2C%20Klarity%20grabbed%20%2470%20million%20in%20a%20Series%20B%20round%20led%20by%20Friedman%20and%20Gross%2C%20with%20participation%20from%20Scale%20Venture%20Partners%2C%20Tola%20Capital%2C%20Picus%20Capital%2C%20Invus%20Capital%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-y-combinator-new-headquarters-office-san-francisco-dogpatch-photos-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EY%20Combinator%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20round%20brings%20Klarity's%20funding%20to%20over%20%2490%20million.%20It%20didn't%20share%20a%20valuation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOf%20our%20portfolio%2C%20they%20were%20by%20far%20the%20fastest%20to%20move%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Aaron%20Fleishman%2C%20a%20Klarity%20investor%20through%20his%20firm%20Tola%20Capital%2C%20an%20early-stage%20venture%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20sink%20or%20swim%20moment%20for%20tech%20companies.%20Just%20as%20the%20internet%20transformed%20industry%20by%20industry%2040%20years%20ago%2C%20the%20rapid%20and%20unstoppable%20march%20of%20AI%20is%20changing%20every%20corner%20of%20society.%20For%20startups%2C%20it%20means%20adopting%20the%20tech%20is%20no%20longer%20optional%3B%20it's%20fast%20becoming%20the%20lifeline%20companies%20need%20to%20stay%20afloat%20in%20a%20competitive%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTheir%20window%20is%20closing%2C%26quot%3B%20Fleishman%20said%20of%20companies%20that%20have%20yet%20to%20adapt.%20%26quot%3BThey%20can%20either%20quickly%20become%20an%20almost%20AI-native%20player%20in%20the%20market%2C%20or%20they're%20going%20to%20fail%20because%20they're%20going%20to%20get%20disrupted.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fb5f0bbd-532a-489a-93f7-c147e6a6b2a4%5C%22%3E'The%20rules%20of%20physics%20have%20changed'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20before%20its%20sabbatical%2C%20Klarity%20was%20well-versed%20in%20natural%20language%20processing%20and%20computer%20vision.%20Its%20software%20turned%20documents%20like%20order%20forms%2C%20invoices%2C%20and%20other%20contracts%20into%20structured%20data%20that%20machines%20can%20understand%20to%20the%20same%20degree%20as%20humans.%20This%20helped%20accountants%20save%20time%20and%20avoid%20costly%20mistakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarly%20versions%20of%20its%20product%20were%20built%20on%20a%20smorgasbord%20of%20third-party%20models%2C%20open-source%20libraries%2C%20and%20models%20that%20Klarity%20trained%20itself.%20But%20Nadhamuni%20said%20its%20own%20models%20were%20limited%20in%20their%20ability%20to%20process%20documents%20they%20had%20never%20seen%20before%20because%20they%20were%20trained%20on%20small%20data%20sets.%20When%20OpenAI%20released%20the%20large%20language%20model%20GPT-3.5%2C%20it%20opened%20new%20possibilities%20for%20tech%20firms%20that%20were%20using%20their%20own%20bespoke%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKlarity's%20sabbatical%20kicked%20off%20with%20a%20three-day%20executive%20team%20gathering%20to%20bring%20them%20on%20the%20same%20page.%20Nadhamuni%20gave%20a%20talk%20on%20generative%20AI%2C%20its%20history%2C%20and%20the%20latest%20breakthroughs%20in%20the%20technology.%20On%20the%20first%20night%2C%20he%20gave%20the%20executives%20homework%3A%20play%20around%20with%20ChatGPT%20on%20personal%20and%20work%20tasks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20way%20we%20framed%20it%20is%2C%20the%20rules%20of%20physics%20have%20changed%2C%26quot%3B%20Nadhamuni%20said.%20%26quot%3BBefore%20we%20ideate%2C%20we%20need%20to%20know%20what%20the%20new%20rules%20are%20to%20really%20get%20a%20sense%20of%20what%20might%20be%20possible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20second%20day%2C%20the%20executives%20huddled%20around%20a%20conference%20room%20table%20and%20threw%20a%20Miro%20board%20up%20on%20a%20screen.%20They%20asked%20themselves%20how%20generative%20AI%20could%20transform%20the%20way%20their%20product%20extracts%20data%20from%20documents%20and%20understand%20the%20nuances%20and%20context%20of%20the%20data.%20They%20pared%20down%20hundreds%20of%20suggestions%20into%20five%20key%20hypotheses.%20If%20the%20new%20tech%20could%20do%20those%20five%20things%2C%20they%20would%20rebuild%20the%20core%20of%20Klarity's%20platform%20using%20generative%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20a%20total%20reset%20was%20worth%20considering%20if%20the%20new%20tech%20was%20better%20at%20understanding%20forms%20and%20data%20that%20it%20hadn't%20seen%20before.%20If%20the%20new%20tech%20made%20onboarding%20easier%20for%20non-experts%2C%20it%20would%20completely%20change%20how%20Klarity%20sells%20to%20enterprises.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEngineers%20split%20into%20small%20groups%20to%20tackle%20each%20hypothesis.%20Nadhamuni%20said%20employees%20had%20%26quot%3Bcomplete%20autonomy%20to%20do%20what%20they%20want%2C%20use%20what%20tools%20they%20want%2C%20obviously%20while%20respecting%20data%20governance%20issues.%26quot%3B%20They%20met%20on%20Fridays%20to%20share%20a%20roundup%20of%20the%20past%20week's%20learnings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENadhamuni%20also%20wrote%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftolacapital.com%2F2023%2F06%2F29%2Fgenerative-ai-sabbatical%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplaybook%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20how%20to%20run%20a%20generative%20AI%20sabbatical%20that's%20available%20on%20Tola%20Capital's%20blog.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20end%20of%20the%20four%20weeks%2C%20Klarity%20was%20ready%20to%20push%20the%20nuclear%20button%20on%20its%20bespoke%20models%20in%20favor%20of%20using%20large%20language%20models.%20The%20GPUs%20it%20used%20are%20gathering%20dust%20in%20an%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Nadhamuni%2C%20a%20sabbatical%20allowed%20the%20company%20to%20move%20at%20the%20speed%20of%20the%20tech's%20rapid%20development.%20It%20shortened%20software%20development%20cycles%20from%20weeks%20and%20days%20to%20hours.%20And%20a%20sabbatical%20forced%20the%20team%20to%20radically%20rethink%20what%20was%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20I%20always%20tell%20my%20team%20is%20assume%20there's%2017%20iterations%20between%20where%20we%20are%20today%20and%20the%20right%20answer%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BDon't%20obsess%20over%20the%20right%20answer%2C%20obsess%20over%20how%20does%20one%20iterate%20quickly%20and%20in%20an%20informed%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstartup-klarity-generative-ai-sabbatical-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727254802000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstartup-klarity-generative-ai-sabbatical-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22For%20four%20weeks%2C%20Klarity%20employees%20froze%20all%20new%20development%20work%20and%20focused%20on%20how%20generative%20AI%20could%20transform%20its%20business.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mrussell%40businessinsider.com%20(Melia%20Russell)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A18%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstartup-klarity-generative-ai-sabbatical-2024-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BA%20Layman%20Cannot...%26quot%3B%3A%20High%20Court%20Questions%20Cops%20On%20Badlapur%20Accused%20Death%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETwo%20days%20after%20Badlapur%20sex%20assault%20accused%20Akshay%20Shinde%20was%20shot%20dead%20in%20custody%2C%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20asked%20tough%20questions%20to%20police%20about%20the%20circumstances%20leading%20to%20the%2024-year-old's%20death.%20The%20court%20was%20hearing%20a%20petition%20by%20Shinde's%20father%2C%20who%20has%20alleged%20that%20his%20son%20was%20killed%20in%20a%20fake%20encounter%20and%20has%20demanded%20a%20probe%20by%20a%20Special%20Investigation%20Team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkshay%20Shinde%20(24)%20was%20accused%20of%20sexually%20assaulting%20two%20minor%20girls%20at%20a%20school%20in%20Badlapur%20where%20he%20worked%20as%20a%20sweeper.%20He%20was%20being%20taken%20from%20Taloja%20Jail%20to%20Badlapur%20Monday%20when%20he%20snatched%20a%20policeman's%20pistol%20and%20opened%20fire.%20An%20assistant%20inspector%20was%20injured%20and%20Shinde%20was%20killed%20in%20retaliatory%20firing%2C%20police%20have%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Revati%20Mohite%20Dere%20and%20Justice%20Prithviraj%20Chavan%2C%20petitioner%20Anna%20Shinde's%20counsel%20said%20the%20accused%20met%20his%20parents%20a%20day%20before%20the%20incident%20and%20was%20in%20no%20mental%20state%20to%20perform%20any%20of%20the%20acts%20alleged%20by%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20present%20case%2C%20the%20police%20is%20deciding%20who%20is%20convicted.%20The%20rule%20of%20law%20must%20prevail.%20This%20is%20setting%20a%20bad%20example%20(and)%20encouraging%20police%20to%20commit%20such...%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20counsel%20said%2C%20seeking%20a%20court-monitored%20probe%20into%20Shinde's%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20court%20questioned%20the%20cause%20of%20death%2C%20the%20state%20government's%20counsel%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3Bbullet%20wound%20on%20the%20left%20thigh%26quot%3B.%20The%20public%20prosecutor%20said%20the%20pistol%20allegedly%20snatched%20by%20Shinde%20could%20be%20unlocked%20in%20two%20ways.%20%26quot%3BOne%20way%20is%20pulling%20the%20upper%20portion%2C%20the%20deceased%20pulled%20the%20slider%2C%20it%20popped%20and%20he%20fired%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%2C%20however%2C%20said%20this%20is%20%26quot%3Bhard%20to%20believe%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BIt%20requires%20strength%20for%20the%20slider%20to%20pop.%20(A)%20layman%20cannot%20fire%20a%20pistol%20unless%20he%20is%20trained%2C%20(a)%20revolver%20is%20different%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%20%26quot%3BAccording%20to%20you%2C%20he%20fired%20three%20bullets.%20Only%20one%20hit%20the%20police%20officer.%20What%20about%20the%20others%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20then%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20accused%20should%20have%20been%20shot%20below%20the%20knee%2C%20but%20the%20state%20government%20responded%20that%20the%20cop%20who%20shot%20him%20%26quot%3Bdid%20not%20have%20time%20to%20think%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BHow%20could%20we%20believe%20that%20the%20police%20could%20not%20overpower%20the%20accused%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdevendra-fadnavis-eknath-shinde-badlapur-sex-assault-case-badla-pura-posters-showing-d-fadnavis-surface-in-mumbai-after-encounter-6645195%5C%22%3EREAD%3A%C2%A0D%20Fadnavis'%20Pic%20On%20'Badla%20Pura'%20Posters%20After%20Sex%20Assault%20Accused%20Shot%20Dead%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTill%20he%20fired%20three%20shots%2C%20where%20were%20you%3F%20You%20could%20have%20easily%20overpowered%20(him).%20It%20is%20not%20like%20he%20was%20a%20hefty%20man.%20This%20can't%20be%20termed%20as%20an%20encounter.%20This%20is%20not%20an%20encounter%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20asked%20if%20there%20were%20CCTV%20cameras%20on%20the%20route.%20The%20state%20government%20responded%20that%20footage%20of%20all%20CCTV%20cameras%20on%20the%20route%20will%20be%20checked.%20%26quot%3BWe%20expect%20the%20investigation%20to%20be%20impartial.%20If%20we%20see%20something%2C%20we%20will%20be%20inclined%20to%20pass%20an%20order%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20questioned%20why%20the%20case%20papers%20have%20not%20been%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20state%20CID%20yet.%20%26quot%3BTime%20is%20of%20the%20essence%20in%20any%20investigation.%20Delay%20will%20lead%20to%20suspicion%20among%20the%20public.%20What%20prevented%20you%20from%20handling%20the%20papers%20yesterday%3F%26quot%3B%20The%20court%20said%20the%20call%20data%20records%20of%20all%20the%20five%20occupants%20of%20the%20police%20vehicle%20--%20four%20officers%20and%20the%20accused%20--%20should%20be%20collected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20custodial%20death%20of%20Akshay%20Shinde%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20has%20set%20off%20a%20hoardings%20spree%20in%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHoardings%20congratulating%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20have%20come%20up%20in%20various%20locations%20in%20Mumbai.%20They%20use%20a%20wordplay%20--%20Badla%20Pura%20(revenge%20complete)%20--%20and%20show%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20holding%20a%20gun.%20These%20hoardings%20do%20not%20carry%20any%20organisation's%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20put%20up%20posters%20of%20its%20own%2C%20claiming%20that%20police%20would%20only%20extort%20money%20during%20the%20Shiv%20Sena-NCP-Congress%20regime%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20but%20cops%20now%20protect%20the%20people.%20The%20Eknath%20Shinde-led%20Shiv%20Sena%20has%20issued%20newspaper%20ads%2C%20describing%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20as%20%26quot%3BDharamvir%26quot%3B%20and%20accusing%20rivals%20of%20politicising%20a%20sensitive%20issue%20like%20rape.%20The%20newspaper%20ad%20also%20has%20a%20cop's%20cap.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaharashtra-government-vs-opposition-over-shooting-of-badlapur-rape-accused-6633668%5C%22%3EREAD%3A%C2%A0Maharashtra%20Government%20Vs%20Opposition%20Over%20Shooting%20Of%20Badlapur%20Rape%20Accused%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20has%20raised%20questions%20about%20the%20police's%20version%20of%20the%20circumstances%20leading%20to%20Shinde's%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20leader%20Sanjay%20Raut%20said%20the%20police's%20version%20was%20suspicious%2C%20but%20there%20was%20no%20need%20to%20show%20sympathy%20for%20Shinde.%C2%A0%26quot%3B....T