i%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETrain%20Operations%3A%20There%20will%20be%20nine%20rakes%20in%20service%2C%20undertaking%2096%20trips%20each%20day.%20Each%20eight-car%20train%20is%20expected%20to%20carry%20around%202%2C500%20passengers.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETrain%20Captains%3A%2048%20train%20captains%20will%20operate%20the%20trains%2C%20which%20can%20technically%20run%20driverless.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20line%20will%20provide%20crucial%20connections%20for%20daily%20commuters%2C%20including%20access%20to%20both%20domestic%20and%20international%20airports.%20Once%20fully%20operational%2C%20the%20Aqua%20Line%20will%20link%20southern%2C%20central%20and%20western%20parts%20of%20Mumbai.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKey%20areas%20along%20this%20line%20include%20Nariman%20Point%2C%20Mumbai%20Central%2C%20Worli%2C%20Dadar%20and%20a%20direct%20connection%20to%20Mumbai%20International%20Airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EMumbai's%20Metro%20price%20structure%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20Aqua%20Line%2C%20the%20fare%20structure%20hasn't%20been%20officially%20confirmed%20yet.%20However%2C%20based%20on%20the%20fare%20structures%20of%20existing%20lines%2C%20it%20is%20expected%20to%20follow%20a%20similar%20range.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere's%20an%20estimated%20fare%20structure%20for%20when%20it%20becomes%20operational%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E0-3%20km%3A%20Rs%2010%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E3-12%20km%3A%20Rs%2020%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E12-18%20km%3A%20Rs%2030%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E18%2B%20km%3A%20Rs%2040%20or%20more%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20passengers%20will%20receive%20paper%20tickets%20with%20a%20QR%20code%2C%20with%20plans%20to%20activate%20NCMC%20cards%20gradually.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20partial%20inauguration%20of%20the%20Metro%203%20corridor%20could%20have%20an%20immediate%20impact%20on%20travel%20within%20the%20city.%20The%20stations%20along%20this%20stretch%20connect%20vital%20locations%20like%20Santacruz%2C%20Marol%20and%20Ghatkopar.%20This%20underground%20line%20is%20expected%20to%20reduce%20road%20traffic%20congestion%2C%20especially%20in%20high-traffic%20areas%20such%20as%20the%20western%20suburbs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOriginally%20planned%20for%20completion%20in%202021%2C%20the%20Aqua%20Line%20faced%20delays%20due%20to%20various%20challenges%2C%20including%20environmental%20concerns%20over%20the%20Aarey%20car%20depot%20and%20slow%20construction%20progress%20by%20contractors.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mumbai%20Metro%20network%20is%20undergoing%20rapid%20expansion%2C%20with%20the%20Aqua%20Line%20being%20one%20of%2014%20planned%20metro%20lines%20designed%20to%20ease%20congestion%20and%20improve%20connectivity%20across%20the%20city.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOther%20current%20and%20upcoming%20Metro%20Lines%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELine%201%20(Blue%20Line)%3A%20The%20first%20metro%20line%2C%20running%20between%20Versova%2C%20Andheri%20and%20Ghatkopar.%20It%20has%2012%20stations%20and%20covers%2011.4%20km.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELine%202A%20(Yellow%20Line)%3A%20This%20partially%20operational%20line%20connects%20Dahisar%20(East)%20to%20DN%20Nagar%20along%20the%20Link%20Road%2C%20covering%2018.6%20km%20with%2017%20stations.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELine%202B%20(Yellow%20Line)%3A%20This%20extension%20of%20Line%202A%20will%20run%20from%20DN%20Nagar%20to%20Mandale.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELine%204%20(Green%20Line)%3A%20Running%20between%20Wadala%20and%20Kasarvadavali%2C%20covering%2032.32%20km%2C%20this%20line%20improves%20connectivity%20through%20central%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELine%205%20(Orange%20Line)%3A%20This%2024.95%20km%20line%20connects%20Thane%2C%20Bhiwandi%20and%20Kalyan.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELine%206%20(Pink%20Line)%3A%20A%2014.47%20km%20line%20linking%20Lokhandwala%20to%20Kanjurmarg%2C%20improving%20east-west%20connectivity%20in%20the%20suburbs.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELine%207%20(Red%20Line)%3A%20This%20line%20is%20operational%20from%20Dahisar%20(East)%20to%20Gundavali%2C%20covering%2016.5%20km%20with%2014%20stations.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELine%209%3A%20An%20extension%20of%20Line%207%20that%20will%20run%20from%20Dahisar%20(East)%20to%20Mira%20Bhayander.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELine%208%20(Airport%20connector)%3A%20A%20proposed%20line%20to%20connect%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%20International%20Airport%20to%20Navi%20Mumbai%20International%20Airport.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELine%2010%20and%20Line%2011%3A%20Planned%20extensions%20to%20improve%20connectivity%20between%20the%20northern%20suburbs%20and%20business%20districts.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELine%2012%3A%20A%20future%20extension%20connecting%20Kalyan%20to%20Taloja%20in%20the%20city's%20outskirts.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELine%2013%20and%20Line%2014%3A%20Proposed%20lines%20that%20will%20extend%20metro%20service%20from%20Mira%20Road%20to%20Virar%20and%20Kanjurmarg%20to%20Badlapur%2C%20further%20reaching%20the%20distant%20suburbs.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727251260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F5n7tih28_mumbai-metro_625x300_25_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fmumbai-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-to-launch-mumbais-first-underground-metro-all-you-need-to-know-6643929%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mumbai's%20first%20and%20Maharashtra's%20second%20underground%20metro%2C%20Line%203%20(Colaba-Bandra-SEEPZ)%2C%20is%20set%20to%20be%20launched%20by%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi%20next%20month.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fmumbai-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-to-launch-mumbais-first-underground-metro-all-you-need-to-know-6643929%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22There's%20a%20new%20reason%20people%20feel%20bad%20about%20the%20economy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20job%20seeker%20looking%20at%20an%20Employment%20page%20i