which%20went%20viral%20on%20social%20media%2C%20prompted%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20seek%20a%20report%20from%20the%20Karnataka%20High%20Court%2C%20which%20was%20submitted%20shortly%20after%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20one%20can%20call%20any%20part%20of%20territory%20of%20India%20as%20'Pakistan'%2C%26quot%3B%20Chief%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20fundamentally%20against%20the%20territorial%20integrity%20of%20the%20nation.%20The%20answer%20to%20sunlight%20is%20more%20sunlight%20and%20not%20to%20suppress%20what%20happens%20in%20court.%20The%20answer%20is%20not%20to%20close%20it%20down.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20taken%20up%20the%20case%20on%20its%20own%20and%20had%20sought%20a%20report%20from%20the%20Karnataka%20High%20Court%20over%20the%20controversial%20remarks.%20A%20five-judge%20bench%20led%20by%20CJI%20Chandrachud%2C%20along%20with%20Justices%20S%20Khanna%2C%20B%20R%20Gavai%2C%20S%20Kant%2C%20and%20H%20Roy%2C%20had%20on%20September%2020%20expressed%20the%20need%20for%20establishing%20clear%20guidelines%20for%20constitutional%20court%20judges%20regarding%20their%20remarks%20in%20court.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCasual%20observational%20may%20indicate%20personal%20biases%20especially%20when%20perceived%20to%20be%20directed%20at%20a%20certain%20gender%20or%20community.%20Thus%20one%20must%20be%20wary%20of%20making%20patriarchal%20or%20misogynistic%20comments.%20We%20express%20our%20serious%20concern%20about%20observations%20on%20a%20certain%20gender%20or%20a%20community%20and%20such%20observations%20are%20liable%20to%20be%20construed%20in%20a%20negative%20light.%20We%20hope%20and%20trust%20that%20the%20responsibilities%20entrusted%20to%20all%20stakeholders%20are%20discharged%20without%20bias%20and%20caution%2C%26quot%3B%20CJI%20Chandrachud%20said%20today.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20bench%20said%20that%20when%20social%20media%20plays%20an%20active%20rol