%20a%20social%20media%20post%2C%20described%20the%20treatment%20of%20the%20woman%2C%20the%20fiancee%20of%20an%20Army%20officer%2C%20as%20%26quot%3Bshameful%20and%20horrendous.%26quot%3B%20General%20Singh%20condemned%20the%20handling%20of%20the%20situation%20by%20the%20Odisha%20Police%20and%20demanded%20immediate%20action%20against%20the%20officers%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEveryone%20must%20listen%20to%20the%20daughter%20of%20a%20retired%20Army%20officer.%20What%20happened%20to%20her%20in%20Bharatpur%20police%20station%20in%20Odisha%20is%20shameful.%20The%20Odisha%20Chief%20Minister%20should%20take%20swift%20action%20against%20the%20police%20personnel%20and%20those%20shielding%20the%20criminals%20in%20uniform%2C%26quot%3B%20General%20Singh%20stated%20in%20his%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20victim's%20account%2C%20she%20was%20allegedly%20thrashed%20and%20sexually%20assaulted%20inside%20Bharatpur%20police%20station%20after%20she%20and%20her%20fiance%20attempted%20to%20file%20a%20complaint%20regarding%20a%20road%20rage%20incident.%20The%20Army%20officer%20was%20allegedly%20illegally%20detained%20by%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20counter-response%2C%20former%20CBI%20Director%20M%20Nageswara%20Rao%2C%20an%20Odisha-cadre%20IPS%20officer%2C%20painted%20a%20different%20picture.%20Mr%20Rao%20disputed%20General%20Singh's%20allegations%20and%20accused%20the%20Army%20officer%20and%20his%20fiancee%20of%20being%20drunk%20and%20behaving%20inappropriately.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20Army%20officer%20and%20his%20fiancee%20consumed%20alcohol%20and%20drove%20through%20the%20city%20late%20at%20night.%20They%20were%20involved%20in%20a%20brawl%20with%20engineering%20students%20and%20later%20created%20a%20scene%20at%20Bharatpur%20police%20station.%20When%20asked%20to%20undergo%20a%20medical%20examination%20and%20blood%20test%2C%20they%20refused%2C%20which%20is%20a%20standard%20part%20of%20the%20investigation%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Rao%20claimed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20defended%20the%20police%2C%20stating%20that%20the%20Odisha%20Police%2C%20which%20manages%20more%20than%20600%20police%20stations%2C%20had%20no%20reason%20to%20misbehave%20with%20visitors%2C%20including%20Army%20personnel.%20Mr%20Rao%20urged%20General%20Singh%20to%20reconsider%20his%20stance%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20is%20improper%20to%20castigate%20the%20police%20for%20the%20actions%20of%20an%20individual%20Army%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20appropriate%20for%20a%20former%20Chief%20of%20Army%20Staff%20and%20Central%20Minister%20to%20jump%20to%20conclusions%20and%20criticize%20the%20police%20for%20the%20alleged%20drunken%20misconduct%20of%20the%20Army%20officer%20and%20his%20fiancee.%20However%2C%20I%20would%20not%20question%20the%20Indian%20Army's%20discipline%20based%20on%20one%20individual's%20actions.%20I%20urge%20the%20Army%20to%20take%20appropriate%20action%20against%20this%20officer%20for%20conduct%20unbecoming%20of%20a%20soldier%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Rao%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20midst%20of%20these%20allegations%2C%20videos%20showing%20the%20couple%20in%20a%20physical%20altercation%20with%20a%20group%20of%20people%20surfaced%20on%20social%20media.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnWhile%20the%20Army%20veterans%20have%20rallied%20around%20the%20officer%20and%20his%20fiancee%2C%20retired%20police%20officers%2C%20including%20Mr%20Rao%2C%20have%20defended%20the%20actions%20of%20the%20Odisha%20Police%20and%20have%20raised%20questions%20about%20the%20behaviour%20of%20the%20couple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20retired%20Army%20officers%20have%20taken%20to%20social%20media%20to%20criticise%20the%20Odisha%20Police%2C%20urging%20the%20Defence%20Ministry%20to%20intervene.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Odisha%20government%20has%20responded%20by%20suspending%20five%20police%20personnel%20involved%20in%20the%20incident%20and%20ordering%20a%20judicial%20inquiry.%20The%20state's%20crime%20branch%20is%20investigating%20the%20allegations%2C%20and%20the%20government%20has%20provided%20security%20to%20the%20Army%20officer%20and%20his%20fiancee%20in%20light%20of%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20a%20meeting%20with%20Odisha's%20Chief%20Minister%20Mohan%20Charan%20Majhi%2C%20the%20woman%20expressed%20relief%20and%20hope%20for%20justice%2C%20stating%20that%20she%20feared%20for%20her%20safety%20given%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20allegations.%20She%20also%20confirmed%20that%20both%20she%20and%20her%20fiance%20had%20accepted%20the%20government's%20offer%20of%20personal%20security%20officers%20(PSOs)%20for%20their%20protection.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727238300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fbuupql68_vk-singh-nageshwar-rao-_625x300_25_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fodisha-army-officer-vk-singh-nageshwar-rao-ex-army-cbi-chiefs-clash-over-alleged-torture-of-woman-at-odisha-police-station-6643772%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Retired%20Army%20Chief%20General%20VK%20Singh%20and%20former%20CBI%20Director%20M%20Nageswara%20Rao%20have%20clashed%20over%20the%20alleged%20torture%20and%20sexual%20assault%20of%20an%20Army%20officer's%20fiancee%20at%20a%20police%20station%20in%20Odisha.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fodisha-army-officer-vk-singh-nageshwar-rao-ex-army-cbi-chiefs-clash-over-alleged-torture-of-woman-at-odisha-police-station-6643772%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20consumer%20commission%20asked%20SBI%20to%20pay%20Rs%2097%20lakh%20as%20compensation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727238143000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113652331%2Cimgsize-10550.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fdriver-stole-rs-63-lakh-from-senior-citize