0and%20friends%20certainly%20will.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Anna%E2%80%99s%20mother%20poignantly%20stated%2C%20it%20is%20our%20collective%20responsibility%20to%20ensure%20that%20no%20other%20family%20or%20parent%20endures%20the%20pain%20they%20are%20experiencing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727186534000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Infographic-website-2-1727184704.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D367326%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amidst%20viral%20conversations%20about%20toxic%20workplaces%20and%20their%20impact%20on%20employee%20well-being%20we%20highlight%20workplaces%20creating%20healthier%20environments.%20By%20integrating%20kindness%20into%20communication%2C%20offering%20flexible%20policies%2C%20and%20encouraging%20open%20dialogue%2C%20some%20organisations%20prioritise%20empathy%20and%20wellness%2C%20demonstrating%20how%20to%20build%20thriving%20workplaces%20where%20employees%20feel%20valued%20and%20supported.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F367326%2Ftoxic-workplaces-solutions-healthy-workplace-work-life-balance-work-pressure-employee-wellbeing%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chhaya%20Kadam%E2%80%99s%20Rise%20From%20Earning%20Rs%20250%2FDay%20to%20Laapataa%20Ladies%20%26amp%3B%20Oscars%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDecades%20ago%2C%20in%202001%2C%20Chhaya%20Kadam%20had%20not%20left%20her%20home%20for%20months.%20%E2%80%9CThat%20year%2C%20my%20father%20and%20brother%20both%20passed%20away%20in%20quick%20succession%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalled.%20Kadam%20was%20looking%20for%20ways%20to%20escape%20her%20rut%2C%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20when%20she%20stumbled%20upon%20a%20newspaper%20advertisement%20for%20an%20acting%20workshop.%20What%20seemed%20like%20an%