%3D%5C%222104%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20man%20reads%20a%20pamphlet%20on%20protecting%20pangolins%20in%20Ngainga%20Village%2C%20Manipur.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pamphlet%20starts%20with%20quotes%20like%20%E2%80%9CLet%20us%20be%20protectors%20of%20GOD%E2%80%99s%20PLAN%20inscribed%20in%20nature%2C%20protectors%20of%20one%20another%20and%20of%20the%20environment%E2%80%9D%20from%20Pope%20Francis%20and%20%E2%80%9CThe%20LORD%20God%20then%20took%20the%20man%20and%20settled%20him%20in%20the%20garden%20of%20Eden%2C%20to%20cultivate%20and%20care%20for%20it%E2%80%9D%20from%20Genesis%202.15.%20The%20message%20seems%20to%20have%20been%20well%20received%20by%20everyone%20in%20the%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIllegal%20wildlife%20trafficking%20in%20Manipur%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManipur%2C%20which%20boasts%20a%20considerable%20population%20of%20the%20Chinese%20pangolin%20(%3Cem%3EManis%20pentadactyla%3C%2Fem%3E)%20has%20been%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20supply%20chain%20for%20illegal%20international%20markets%20across%20Southeast%20Asia.%20It%20continues%20to%20be%20the%20state%20with%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20pangolin%20seizures%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS2665910720300049%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2020%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20on%20Science%20Direct%20states%20that%2021%25%20of%20pangolin%20seizures%20between%202009%20and%202018%20in%20India%20were%20from%20Manipur%2C%20followed%20by%20Mizoram%20and%20Assam.%20An%20average%20Chinese%20pangolin%20has%20between%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS235198941930424X%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E509%20and%20664%20scales%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20a%20combined%20dry%20weight%20of%20about%20467%20grams.%20Imagine%20the%20number%20of%20pangolins%20it%20took%20to%20produce%203%2C248%20kilograms%20of%20pangolin%20scales%20that%20have%20been%20recovered%20in%20Manipur%20alone%2C%20and%20this%20is%20only%20from%20what%20has%20been%20reported%20or%20seized%20by%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20pangolins%20that%20are%20exchanged%20in%20the%20borders.%20Other%20wildlife%2C%20including%20marine%20trophies%20too%20reach%20Manipur%20as%20a%20transit%20to%20the%20international%20market%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jose%20Louies%2C%20the%20CEO%20and%20Chief%20of%20Enforcement%20at%20WTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETeam%20WTI%20has%20also%20begun%20training%20border%20enforcement%20agencies%20and%20forest%20officials%20to%20help%20curb%20the%20trade.%20The%20trainings%20involve%20wildlife%20article%20identification%20and%20understanding%20the%20various%20facets%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F333222%2Fanne-wright-conservationist-wildlife-protection-act-reserves-project-tiger-legacy-raza-kazmi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWildlife%20(Protection)%20Act%2C%201972%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20be%20able%20to%20better%20investigate%20a%20case%20and%20achieve%20a%20better%20conviction%20rate%20for%20offenders%20in%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202072px)%20100vw%2C%202072px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCommunity-event-_-angolin-Project-_-Manipur-_-Madhumay-Mallik_11zon-1727101599.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222072%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22People%20participate%20in%20a%20community%20event%20centred%20around%20the%20protection%20of%20pangolins.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCommunity-event-_-angolin-Project-_-Manipur-_-Madhumay-Ma