Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20had%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20case%20stayed%20in%20the%20spotlight.%20So%2C%20Anjali%20and%20Jaishankar%20met%20with%20editors%20from%20various%20media%20organisations%2C%20who%20supported%20them%20by%20consistently%20reporting%20on%20the%20case.%20Anjali%20particularly%20mentions%20The%20Indian%20Express%20%E2%80%94%20who%20sent%20a%20reporter%20for%20every%20hearing%20%E2%80%94%20and%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%223%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EBuild%20pressure%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20made%20sure%20the%20hearings%20weren%E2%80%99t%20delayed%20by%20getting%20letters%20from%20influential%20people%20like%20Narayana%20Murthy%20and%20Kris%20Gopalakrishnan%20of%20Infosys%20and%20senior%20IIM%20alumni%2C%20which%20they%20sent%20to%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%224%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EBe%20present%20on%20the%20ground%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20every%20hearing%2C%20either%20Jaishankar%20or%20Anjali%20would%20travel%20from%20Mysuru%20to%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri.%20They%20would%20post%20the%20hearing%20dates%20in%20online%20alumni%20groups%3B%20alumni%20who%20were%20free%20on%20the%20date%2C%20would%20also%20attend.%20A%20group%20of%20IIM%20Lucknow%20student%20volunteers%20took%20turns%20to%20be%20present%20at%20the%20hearings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%225%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ERaise%20funds%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThanks%20to%20their%20extensive%20network%2C%20they%20were%20able%20to%20raise%20funds%20for%20all%20the%20legal%20and%20travel%20expenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%226%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ENever%20give%20up%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20importantly%2C%20despite%20the%20fight%20being%20solitary%20and%20difficult%2C%20they%20never%20lost%20hope.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Anjali%20and%20Jaishankar%2C%20travelled%20to%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%20at%20least%2010%20times%20during%20the%20trial.%20Their%20journey%20involved%20taking%20a%20bus%20to%20Bengaluru%2C%20a%20flight%20to%20Delhi%2C%20then%20to%20Lucknow%2C%20followed%20by%20a%20cab%20to%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20pushed%20them%20to%20fight%20for%20a%20boy%20they%20had%20never%20met%3F%20Didn%E2%80%99t%20they%20ever%20feel%20bogged%20down%3F%20%E2%80%9CCertainly.%20Some%20days%20were%20tough.%20At%20times%2C%20it%20seemed%20like%20an%20impossible%20task.%20We%20were%20carrying%20a%20heavy%20responsibility%20that%20we%20had%20to%20fulfil.%20We%20had%20to%20give%20our%20best%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Anjali.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20IIM%20alumni%20volunteers%2C%20various%20people%20%E2%80%94%20complete%20strangers%20%E2%80%94%20wrote%20in%20and%20helped%2C%20which%20was%20a%20major%20support%2C%20they%20say.%20To%20honour%20his%20memory%2C%20on%20Manjunath%E2%80%99s%20first%20death%20anniversary%2C%20the%20trust%20inaugurated%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20Right%20To%20Information%20Act%20(RTI)%20helpline.%20The%20helpline%20ran%20for%20three%20years%2C%20helping%20thousands%20of%20citizens%20use%20the%20act%20to%20fight%20corruption.%20They%20also%20established%20the%20Manjunath%20Shanmugam%20Integrity%20Award%20to%20honour%20individuals%20who%20fought%20against%20systemic%20corruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20fight%20for%20justice%20continued%20until%202015%2C%20as%20the%20convicts%20appealed%20in%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20in%202009%2C%20followed%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%202015.%20While%20the%20High%20Court%20upheld%20the%20convictions%2C%20it%20commuted%20Mittal%E2%80%99s%20death%20sentence%20to%20life%20imprisonment.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20also%20upheld%20the%20convictions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%