ithout%20our%20earphones%20or%20power%20banks%2C%20I%20wanted%20the%20user%20to%20form%20a%20companionship%20with%20Novocarry.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENovocarry%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98portable%20cooling%20solution%E2%80%99%2C%20is%20apt%20to%20store%20medications%20like%20insulin%20that%20require%20refrigeration%20during%20transport.%20And%20it%20does%20this%20while%20proving%20to%20be%20discreet%2C%20convenient%2C%20and%20reliable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ENovocarry%3A%20A%20potential%20solution%20for%20diabetic%20patients%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20design%20student%E2%80%99s%20journey%20is%20a%20mark%20of%20serendipity%3B%20right%20from%20her%20foray%20into%20the%20bachelor%20in%20design%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F114959%2Fmigrant-workers-sleep-easy-design-innovation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eindustrial%20design%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20NID%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20initially%20preparing%20for%20my%20law%20entrance%20exam%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%94%20to%20winning%20the%20James%20Dyson%20Award%202024%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%9CNovocarry%20started%20out%20as%20a%20classroom%20project.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPerceived%20as%20the%20gold%20standard%20for%20design%20awards%2C%20the%20James%20Dyson%20recognition%20fosters%20problem-solving%20attitudes%2C%20encouraging%20students%20to%20broaden%20their%20innovative%20minds.%20Recalling%20her%20introduction%20to%20the%20Dyson%20world%2C%20Komal%20recalls%20seeing%20the%20famous%20hairdryer.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20fascinated%20with%20the%20technology%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20points%20out.%20Her%20excitement%20is%20still%20palpable%20through%20the%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20led%20to%20another%2C%20taking%20Komal%20down%20a%20rabbit%20hole%20of%20videos%20that%20dissected%20the%20hair%20dryer%E2%80%99s%20ergonomic%20design.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20hooked.%20It%20was%20a%20Eureka!%20moment%20that%20ha