ont%20costs%20by%20as%20much%20as%2040%25%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20multiple%20ventures%20at%20the%20time%20that%20decided%20to%20get%20into%20the%20business%20of%20manufacturing%20EVs%20and%20chargers%2C%20Pulkit%20and%20Siddharth%20ventured%20into%20battery-swapping%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlthough%20manufacturing%20chargers%20and%20vehicles%20is%20an%20exciting%20field%2C%20we%20chose%20to%20focus%20on%20addressing%20key%20challenges%20such%20as%20range%20anxiety%2C%20charging%20downtime%2C%20and%20high%20costs.%20By%20partnering%20with%20over%20ten%20leading%20OEMs%20(original%20equipment%20manufacturers)%20working%20on%20battery%20development%20and%20manufacturing%2C%20we%20can%20stay%20ahead%20of%20the%20curve%20with%20changing%20technology.%20We%20always%20have%20the%20option%20to%20evaluate%20and%20choose%20from%20the%20best%20battery%20technology%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FBattery-Smart-Swapping-Station-14-1726583256.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22EV%20battery%20swapping%20technology%20works%20better%20than%20straight%20charging%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FBattery-Smart-Swapping-Station-14-1726583256.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FBattery-Smart-Swapping-Station-14-1726583256-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FBattery-Smart-Swapping-Station-14-1726583256-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FBattery-Smart-Swapping-Station-14-1726583256-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FBattery-Smart-Swapping-Station-