0comprehensive%20protocols%20that%20prioritise%20the%20safety%20of%20both%20drivers%20and%20station%20operators.%20They%20have%20done%20this%20by%20using%20their%20BMS%2C%20which%20allows%20them%20to%20track%20in%20real-time%20the%20critical%20parameters%20of%20the%20batteries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20ensure%20that%20all%20batteries%20on%20our%20network%20have%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F341081%2Fiit-guwahati-phd-satyam-develops-affordable-iot-enabled-water-quality-purity-monitoring-device%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIoT%20device%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20facilitates%20real-time%20monitoring%20of%20critical%20parameters%2C%20such%20as%20voltage%2C%20temperature%2C%20and%20current.%20We%20also%20offer%2024%C3%977%20on-call%20support%20to%20our%20drivers%20and%20partners.%20In%20addition%2C%20we%20make%20sure%20that%20all%20station%20partners%20and%20drivers%20on%20board%20our%20network%20receive%20mandatory%20training%20programmes%20and%20refresher%20courses%20on%20proper%20battery%20management%2C%20storage%2C%20handling%2C%20and%20emergency%20response%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFuture%20of%20EV%20battery%20swapping%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.psmarketresearch.com%2Fmarket-analysis%2Findia-electric-vehicle-battery-swapping-market%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPrescient%20and%20Strategic%20Intelligence%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20market%20research%20venture%2C%20the%20Indian%20EV%20battery-swapping%20market%20stood%20at%20an%20estimated%20%2410.2%20million%20in%202022.%20This%20market%20is%20expected%20to%20reach%20%2461.57%20million%20by%202030%E2%80%93growth%20at%20a%20CAGR%20of%2025.20%25%20from%202022%20to%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20India%E2%80%99s%20last%20financial%20year%2C%20Indians